Comment: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いたずらに迷う　数奇な生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}止め処無い孤独　戻せない針が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}チク　タク　チク　タク
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}縁と怨を重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}薄気味の悪いハイソなジオラマで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.22,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}息を潜め　空虚な旅の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}tick tack tick tack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.60,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}お帰り　天国と地獄の庭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ナイト　デイ　アフター　トゥモロー　回れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今が全部　無意味だろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.49,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}現実を見る眼を曇らせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}遊魔ヶ時へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.49,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}甘ったるい安寧は夢の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仮面越しの愛も偽物に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.25,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}この難解な世界　難解な世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.50,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心融け会えばいずれ暴かれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.04,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}アイムノットルーニー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.88,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}別々に刻んだ秒針の行く先は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑ってるの日々？泣いてるの日々？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:34.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}隠し合った傷跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ハイドアンドシークで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.01,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さあさ探して頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.48,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}邪魔しないで頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被命运搅弄  多舛的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无边的孤独中  只有单行的秒针
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.09,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}滴  答  滴  答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.84,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}刻下一道道因果与憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.72,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}令人不适的奢侈的道德困境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}屏住呼吸  在空虚旅途的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}滴  答  滴  答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.60,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}欢迎回到天堂与地狱的庭园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}白昼  夜晚  明天  后天  来回交替
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使现在并无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}眯起看向现实的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}游魔之时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}甜蜜的安宁似同梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}面具下的爱也化作虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.25,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}面对这难解的世界  难解的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只要我们心灵合一  或许就能找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.04,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我并不是疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}各自行走的秒针所要抵达的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是充满笑声还是泪水的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:34.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}互相遮掩住的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.72,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就请你用捉迷藏的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}来找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不要妨碍我们
Comment: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.14,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From the day we promised
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:06.10,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}漕ぎ始めた小さなボート
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:09.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Until we get to the place we dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:11.69,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向かず along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:14.31,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}To go straight 息を揃え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは同じ歌を歌う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:19.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}赤なら止まれ no rush
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:22.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz it’s a long long way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:26.16,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the heavy rain is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:27.99,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We really don’t care
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.25,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾いた風も追い風に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:33.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いっそ遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.34,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The gate is open
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:37.96,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遠ざかる skyline
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:39.59,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}動き出した life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:43.43,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The sunrise 登るまで seize the night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.64,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I keep dreaming of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:50.39,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Moonlit 僕らの描いた story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:53.98,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Prove it その日までの journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:57.86,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How many miles can we go forward tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.55,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\bord1}How many miles can we go forward tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.14,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们立下誓言的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:06.10,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的木船驶向旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:09.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向着我们梦中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:11.69,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无需留念  一心向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:14.31,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迈着相同的步子前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.07,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们异口同声地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:19.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}红灯就歇歇  不必着急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:22.66,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们要走的路还很长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:26.16,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使暴风雨将要到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:27.99,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们也不会在意分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不如就乘上干燥的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:33.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}飞向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.34,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}门已经敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:37.96,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无垠的天际线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:39.59,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生命开始转动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:43.43,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抓住夜晚  跟随日出的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.64,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在梦中呼唤黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:50.39,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}月光洒下我们描绘的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:53.98,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}证明我们漫漫旅途的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:57.86,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今夜的我们  还能前进几里？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.55,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\bord1}今夜的我们  还能前进几里？
